  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Crystal Keepers </strong>is a cooperative action game for up to 4 players, where you will face  waves of relentless enemies, including challenging bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive as a team by creating strategies, discovering synergies, and unleashing your full potential with coordinated attacks, abilities, and items to make it to the end!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492560/extras/a16e970c9ab3640d1b4ebe73beec2ee8.poster.avif?t=1748386525\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492560/extras/a16e970c9ab3640d1b4ebe73beec2ee8.webm?t=1748386525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492560/extras/a16e970c9ab3640d1b4ebe73beec2ee8.mp4?t=1748386525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choose your class</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select from a variety of classes to suit your playstyle and create creative builds to make each match unique.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492560/extras/f1e913c7c0dda8e90005262a1125b80d.poster.avif?t=1748386525\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492560/extras/f1e913c7c0dda8e90005262a1125b80d.webm?t=1748386525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492560/extras/f1e913c7c0dda8e90005262a1125b80d.mp4?t=1748386525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Make your character</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your hero with a unique combination of abilities and passives, acquired as you level up, allowing for creative strategies and powerful synergies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492560/extras/ff8f3376a531c6ea94e112b7977e18eb.poster.avif?t=1748386525\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492560/extras/ff8f3376a531c6ea94e112b7977e18eb.webm?t=1748386525\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3492560/extras/ff8f3376a531c6ea94e112b7977e18eb.mp4?t=1748386525\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between waves, acquire items with no inventory restrictions to further enhance your build. With six rarity levels for items, cards, and enemies, every match offers a unique experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase items to dominate the battlefield and evolve your Guardian. Play solo or with friends and dive into this adventure!</p>",
